text.tspan: IBM UK and Ireland CTO, an IBM Distinguished Engineer, a Master
Inventor and Member of the IBM Academy of Technology
Andy will take us on a tour of some of his exciting IoT projects,
starting in the living lab he has created at his home on the
Isle of Wight, including his electronic mousetraps. Via tweeting
ferries and animatronic dinosaurs, we end up at Marwell zoo in
Hampshire, controlling the heating in the animal houses.
Free to attend. RVSP for drinks and pizza!
